The Koni shocks are what VW sold as a heavy-duty shock option.  They  
are adjustable (soft to firm), and have a lifetime warranty for the  
purchaser and are repairable by Koni.

> $100 for a shock is cheap?

Taken in context, yes.  These are fantastic shocks, and the last  
you'll ever have to buy for your Bus.

